She manages to escape but is unfortunately moved down by a speeding vehicle driven by Sunil. This accident renders her visually impaired. The guilt-ridden Anand wishes to apologize to Vidya for his wrongdoings. Will Anand's apology be accepted? Will Vidya be able to reunite with her brother?
